  <!-- EN: desired -->
  <VME_Fire_Desired.label>渴望</VME_Fire_Desired.label>
  <!-- EN: The warmth of ash, the light of embers, scintillating flame is an awesome sight to behold.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color>\n - Colonists get moods bonuses depending on the number of active fires on the map. Campfires, torches, Stone Campfires from Vanilla Furniture Expanded - Core and Hearths from Vanilla Factions Expanded - Vikings also count. -->
  <VME_Fire_Desired.description>温暖的灰尘、明亮的余烬以及闪烁的火花，这些景象看起来真是不可思议。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;游戏效果：&lt;/color&gt;\n - 殖民者会依据地图上的火焰数量来获得心情增益。篝火、火把、原版家具扩展的石制篝火以及维京派系扩展的石炉也包括在内。</VME_Fire_Desired.description>
  <!-- EN: No fires nearby -->
  <VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.0>附近没有火焰</VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.0>
  <!-- EN: Very few fires -->
  <VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.1>极少的火焰</VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.1>
  <!-- EN: Small fires -->
  <VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.2>少量的火焰</VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.2>
  <!-- EN: Saw fires -->
  <VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.3>看到了火焰</VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.3>
  <!-- EN: Amazing fires -->
  <VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.4>美妙的火焰</VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.4>
  <!-- EN: Beautiful fires -->
  <VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.5>绚丽的火焰</VME_Fire_Desired.comps.0.thoughtStageDescriptions.5>
  
  <!-- EN: despised -->
  <VME_Fire_Despised.label>厌恶</VME_Fire_Despised.label>
  <!-- EN: There is nothing as disgusting as an out of control fire. The flames shall be avoided by any means necessary, for their destructive power is unmatched.\n\n<color=#E5E54C>Gameplay effect:</color>\n - Colonists get negative moods depending on the number of active fires on the map. Campfires, torches, Stone Campfires from Vanilla Furniture Expanded - Core and Hearths from Vanilla Factions Expanded - Vikings also count. -->
  <VME_Fire_Despised.description>没有什么比失控的大火更令人糟心的了。火焰的破坏力无与伦比，我们必须通过任何手段来阻止火灾的出现。\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;游戏效果：&lt;/color&gt;\n - 殖民者会依据地图上的火焰数量来获得心情减益。篝火、火把、原版家具扩展的石制篝火以及维京派系扩展的石炉也包括在内。</VME_Fire_Despised.description>
